					<div class=entry-title><a href=#>Using Cobalt - Edusim on the Classroom Interactive Whiteboard</a></div>
<br>
Formal training and development packages are currently being designed based on teacher and classroom input.  If you would like to be a formal "Edusim Classroom" and help us pilot Edusim please email rich.white(at)greenbush.org and we will provide you with directions to become involved in a formal way with this project.
